# Week 04 - Monitoring & Database Services

## Learning Objectives

Learn how to monitor cloud systems and manage databases.

## Activities

## Amazon CloudWatch

Practiced:

- Monitoring metrics.
- Reviewing logs.
- Creating alarms.


## Amazon RDS

Learned:

- Managed database services.
- Database deployment.
- Application-database connectivity.


## Key Outcomes

- Understand cloud monitoring.
- Manage database resources on AWS.
